[{"id":"cloche-1dz","title":"Show parent/child run relationships in web UI","description":"With workflow steps, runs now have parent/child relationships. Two changes needed:

1. Run Details page: add a header link to the parent run and a section listing child runs with links.
2. Runs list page: visually group parent/child runs together (accordion, tree nesting, or similar). Important: child runs are often more important than parents since the active work happens in children while parents block waiting. The visual design should prioritize children even when grouped under a parent."}]
